title: 2 micro distilleries added to Bourbon tour
text:
Published By: Louisville Courier-Journal: Lifestyle - Today 
Two distilleries have been added to the Kentucky Bourbon Trail Craft Tour, bringing the total number of micro distilleries included to 10.
